    "description": "<p>DORF KETAL CHEMICALS PTE. LTD.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dorf Ketal develops, manufactures, sells and services specialty process chemicals and additives for oil and gas exploration and production, oil refining and petrochemicals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We built our reputation for innovation with unique chemistry and expert&nbsp; analytical support that overcome the challenges imposed by heavy crudes, generating documented profit improvement for our customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Name Dorf Ketal Reflects our Focus on <u>D</u>riling, <u>Olefins</u>, <u>R</u>efining and <u>F</u>uels</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In just 15 years we have become one of the world&#39;s fastest-growing manufacturers of formulation-based specialty chemicals for refineries and petrochemical plants.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Today Dorf Ketal is a leading supplier of performance-engineered specialty chemical programs in the Asia Pacific, Mddle East and Europe as well as the world leader in organic titanate and organic zirconate catalyst chemistries.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n",
